{"tid":899882,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"西霉又鬧香港人歧視支那蝗蟲","createTime":"2018-11-12T20:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T01:29:08.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"09d376e8cdd2f0f054c9563ad4280d608e527ffe","tid":899882,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T20:16:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.economist.com/node/21752678?fsrc=FacebookInstant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fnode%2F21752678%3Ffsrc%3DFacebookInstant&d=tLhEsJyQ7Lucld1prbwvH0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e9909dcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.economist.com/node/21752678?fsrc=FacebookInstant</a> <br />\n<br />\n西霉出一篇報導，起碼要經過三四個人 - 主要記者同埋researcher做訪問搜集資料，寫完後要畀編輯睇過先出得。 就算寫嗰個係支那人，佢上頭多數係西人。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/21/CzYQDK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2FCzYQDK.png&h=2129d510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n親中未必係支那。<br />\n好似呢篇報導個標題：「真係多謝晒當奴侵！中國科技女王今年蝕咗96億美元」<br />\n<br />\n之後篇文鬧侵，搞到支那女人。<br />\n<br />\n作者除咗有支那女人，重有猶太人，應該係女人。"},{"pid":"d01fc2c2e15e28c99f39f09e5ad511ad04f369e5","tid":899882,"uid":199145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T20:29:04.000Z","msg":"Economist 一聽已經係華爾街走狗你話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd8696f98351693328a1bff6232350756c995d4","tid":899882,"uid":165711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T23:22:05.000Z","msg":"邊撚個tech queen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850aeba6590f689287f5d5eec75363371bcd64a6","tid":899882,"uid":212119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:29:08.000Z","msg":"venus weng<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=